2164.subject: MLML
2164.descrlong: MLML211:Eco Mar Bird/Mamm-  Community approach to the ecology of marine birds and mammals using experimental sampling methodology. Examines the distribution, abundance, trophic ecology, and behavior of birds and mammals in Elkhorn Slough and Monterey Bay. Offered through Moss Landing Marine Laboratories (MLML); contact SEP program office for MLML registration procedures.
